{"id":601761,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/【立此存照】社会主义核心价值观的神学诠释/","date":"2018-12-17T10:07:28Z","modified":"2018-12-18T05:40:25Z","title":"【立此存照】社会主义核心价值观的神学诠释","content":"<p>近日，有网友晒出一本“奇书”——《社会主义核心价值观的神学诠释》的封面以及部分目录，该书中国数字时代未搜索到网上贩售的有关信息，或为内部发行，从一篇刊于“天光（天主教北京教区天光网站）”的<a href=\"http://www.tianguangbao.org/2017.11.1/11.htm\">文章</a>得知，该书作者为王和平。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-601784\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平1.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平1-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平1-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>从有限的目录内容来看，该书试图从天主教理论中找到与“社会主义核心价值观”的对应性，基于天主教信仰角度来谈对社会主义核心价值观的理解与诠释。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-601785\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平2.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平2-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/王和平2-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>在此之前，中国数字时代还报道过“社会主义核心价值观”与中国式佛教、道教的“相互融合”，核心价值观由此得到“生动解释”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%9B%E6%B3%95.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"370\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/4b2ac0eely1frinjcdbs7j20zk0qogpw.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"365\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%82\">核心价值观</a></p>\n<p><span id=\".E3.80.90.E7.AB.8B.E6.AD.A4.E5.AD.98.E7.85.A7.E3.80.91.E5.A6.87.E7.A7.91.E4.B8.8D.E7.AC.A6.E5.90.88.E6.A0.B8.E5.BF.83.E4.BB.B7.E5.80.BC.E8.A7.82\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E5%A6%87%E7%A7%91%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%82/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">【立此存照】妇科不符合核心价值观</a></span></p>\n<p><span id=\".E3.80.90.E5.9B.BE.E8.AF.B4.E5.A4.A9.E6.9C.9D.E3.80.91.E9.81.93.E6.95.99.E6.80.9D.E6.83.B3.E4.B8.8E.E6.A0.B8.E5.BF.83.E4.BB.B7.E5.80.BC.E8.A7.82.E8.9E.8D.E5.90.88\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/%E3%80%90%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%91%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8E%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%82%E8%9E%8D%E5%90%88/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">【图说天朝】道教思想与核心价值观融合</a></span></p>\n<p><span id=\".E3.80.90.E5.9B.BE.E8.AF.B4.E5.A4.A9.E6.9C.9D.E3.80.91.E7.A4.BE.E4.BC.9A.E4.B8.BB.E4.B9.89.E4.BB.B7.E5.80.BC.E8.A7.82.E4.B8.8E.E4.BD.9B.E6.B3.95\" class=\"mw-headline\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%E3%80%90%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%91%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%9B%E6%B3%95/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">【图说天朝】社会主义价值观与佛法</a></span></p></blockquote>\n","author":978,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[15028,37257,26544,9707,24636]}